      "note": "<h3>What's new</h3> <ul> <li>Users can now upload data in a folder structure and view folder contents in the File Explorer.</li> <li>Project Service Request feature implemented to support Project-based services access requests and notifications.</li> <li>Development for back-end storage of file metadata to support advanced File Query feature.</li> </ul> <h3>Bug Fixes</h3> <ul> <li>Fixed bug causing files to display incorrectly when switching between folders in the File Explorer. </li> </ul> <h3>Improvements</h3> <ul> <li>Updated Portal terminology from File Manifest to File Attribute.</li> <li>Improved display responsivity in tables during Portal window re-sizing.</li>  </ul>"
