      "note": "<h3>What’s new</h3> <ul> <li>Data deletion protocol implemented for moving data into zone-specific Trash Bins.</li><li>A Project File Manifest Template creation and file attachment feature for describing and categorizing data can now be created and configured by Administrators.</li><li>A File Manifest can be attached by file uploaders or Project Administrator in the Green Room.</li><li>External open-source services of XWiki and Guacamole were deployed and configured with VRE Portal for documentation management and workbench initiation.</li><li>Content Previewer feature now allows users to view file structures inside ZIP files within the File Explorer.</li></ul> <h3>Bug Fixes</h3> <ul> <li> Email notifications now can be sent by Platform Administrators to specific platform users from the Administrators Console.</li><li>Portal release notes are now available in the Portal page footer.</li> <li>Fixed audit logs bug that was displaying incorrect file activities time.</li> </ul>"
